    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the first was Meir.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mosha. ?] And the last one, the last was my sister, Goldie, came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I was here in Canada, I find my brother [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Label. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know he's alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wrote.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wrote.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I gave letters to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She went to Russia lots of times, you know, for the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she came back and she said, they said they don't know even where his bones.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They don't know if he's alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I knew he's not alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother was wrote letters and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was in jail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that he got married in [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Latvia ?] with a [INAUDIBLE] from [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Latvia ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he start writing letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he find letters whose people told him, you have your mother's looking for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he started writing letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's the way we-- they find him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was in Pole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "From Russia, he came to Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she was-- she went teaching Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When he didn't-- a man is not working, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know why. ?] But he felt so low.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then my mother wrote me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Please, if I can take him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I was not rich here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's the first time when we bought a store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I couldn't refuse my mom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I said, I can take him out alone.",
